{"tid":1010361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[政府又可以 save  $4000]彩虹道街市 露宿者猝死地上","createTime":"2019-02-06T03:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T13:11:44.000Z","uid":65346,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5d54fbb9f3778d4a37849e34ab0464bba35e972c","tid":1010361,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T03:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n新蒲崗彩虹道街市，早上7時許，一名中年男子，被發現昏迷在街市通道上，全無反應，救護員接報趕至現場，惟證實男子已告<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">死亡</span>，死者手機及財物未失，相信為一名露宿者，懷疑熟睡期間突然猝死，警方正調查其死亡原因。"},{"pid":"3f15cf12ad261b7c4fe43655ff38adc70e5de804","tid":1010361,"uid":34251,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T03:05:18.000Z","msg":"政府 : 市民勿一窩蜂死亡"},{"pid":"b05d9cece0e2bf81c008896339fe0ca8e0560e83","tid":1010361,"uid":69886,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T03:06:09.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2464dc9338f9b89e30add39bb81d971f0b5460","tid":1010361,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170223/_2017022308472334971.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170223%2F_2017022308472334971.jpg&h=be603270&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1bfe7ec299c544b03db108d0442ab40b9effa55","tid":1010361,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1f2464dc9338f9b89e30add39bb81d971f0b5460","tid":1010361,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170223/_2017022308472334971.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih